precis:
Enactment of the PROVINCIAL EMERGENCIES FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER
NO. 20 - which declares a certain provincial emergency to be of concern to
the federal government and authorizes the provision of financial
assistance in respect thereof (flooding in ALBERTA in June, 1996).
